Kotlin is a programming language used for Development

1. Go to https://kotlinlang.org/ and in the Try Kotlin Simplest version, type:

package org.kotlinlang.play

fun main() 
{
    println("Hello World by Usaid Bin Rehan")
}

2. In the An Object-oriented Hello, type:

class HelloWorldClass(val name: String) 
{
    fun HelloWorldFunction() 
    {
        println("Hello World by $name")
    }
}

fun main(args: Array<String>) 
{
    HelloWorldClass("Usaid Bin Rehan").HelloWorldFunction()
}
